                                    <material type="stone">Dolerite</material> <note><q>Spotted dolerite with 5-10 per cent albitized feldspar phenocrysts (1-10mm)</q> (Edwards 2007, 219-220).</note>
                                    <objectType key="monument">Pillar</objectType> 
                                    <dimensions unit='m'>
                                        <height>1.48</height>
                                        <width>0.56</width>
                                        <depth>0.405</depth>
